{"tid":1794372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共借聯合國過橋將公務員「幹部化」！","createTime":"2019-12-23T05:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T13:39:09.000Z","uid":144018,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7c59ce7e8636667cd8b0d5f2ef8063c3d2e1c320","tid":1794372,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今日（23日）在「國家推送香港青年赴聯合國任職發布會」中宣布，將有5名特區政府青年公務員到聯合國不同機構任職，分別來自行政署、香港天文台、機電工程署及廉政公署。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，今次是特區官員<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首次以中國人員身份、在國家推薦下到聯合國任職</span></span>，是國家支持香港青年在國際舞台，施展才能的嶄新計劃，對香港來說是重大突破<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n擺明係想將公務員「幹部化」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前葉國謙先話「公務員廣義上是國家幹部」公務員<br />\n依家就借聯合國名正言順咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb948c79d79f6c56f1138ebfdeaa2b9cd46ed779","tid":1794372,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e99b5cd3af0b35164170e4cd03dafbb553fa5a","tid":1794372,"uid":28252,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"佢係用中國官員身份入去就gg, 可以煲大佢地直接結束一國兩際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4049f58064c887cd1085a74ca54fee30d5078e51","tid":1794372,"uid":146030,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"所以公務員冇一個係無辜<br />\n根本係幫政府助紂為虐嘅工具"},{"pid":"7f6f7469b3ead2fafbdccc492499e61ef0b79a21","tid":1794372,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95e99b5cd3af0b35164170e4cd03dafbb553fa5a","tid":1794372,"uid":28252,"like":22,"dislik